org.glyptodon.guacamole.protocols

Class ProtocolInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glyptodon.guacamole.protocols.ProtocolInfo

  • public class ProtocolInfo
extends Object
    Describes a protocol and all parameters associated with it, as required by a protocol plugin for guacd. This class allows known parameters for a protocol to be exposed to the user as friendly fields.
    Author:
    Michael Jumper
